OL,3,CTerminally ill man waits two months
OL,4,Cfor social security support
OL,6,FA Jersey man is calling for terminally
OL,7,Fill islanders to be treated with "a
OL,8,Flittle more dignity, care, and speed"
OL,9,Fby the Social Security department.
OL,11,FWayne Lawson feels as though he has
OL,12,F"fallen through the cracks of
OL,13,Fbureaucracy" after it took him seven
OL,14,Fweeks to receive any kind of income
OL,15,Fsupport from Social Services.
OL,17,FDiagnosed with terminal cancer in
OL,18,FOctober, the company Wayne worked for
OL,19,Fwas liquidated just a week later.
