OL,3,CTerminally ill man waits two months
OL,4,Cfor social security support
OL,6,FDespite making immediate applications
OL,7,Ffor both income support and
OL,8,Fimpairment, it was almost two months
OL,9,Fbefore either claim was accepted - and
OL,10,Fhe continues to wait for his
OL,11,Fimpairment payment to be processed.
OL,13,FDuring this period, Wayne reports he
OL,14,Fhad to fill out five 30+ page forms
OL,15,Fwith information for three different
OL,16,Fpeople within the Social Security
OL,17,Fdepartment.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/9
