OL,3,CTerminally ill man waits two months
OL,4,Cfor social security support
OL,6,FLiving off just #283 per week - a
OL,7,Fshort-term sickness payment to support
OL,8,Fhis cancer treatment - Wayne says the
OL,9,Fprocess has caused him significant
OL,10,Femotional upset at a time when he
OL,11,Fshould be focusing on his health,
OL,12,Ffriends, and family.
OL,14,FWayne reflects: "What you're trying to
OL,15,Fdo is deal with your prognosis and
OL,16,Fyour health issues. You're also
OL,17,Fdealing with your friends and family
OL,18,Fbecause they're suffering what I'm
OL,19,Fsuffering and they're hurting.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/9
