OL,3,CTerminally ill man waits two months
OL,4,Cfor social security support
OL,6,FWayne adds: "I've always worked, I've
OL,7,Falways paid into the system, I've paid
OL,8,Fmy taxes, I've paid my social security
OL,9,F- and you have to battle to get the
OL,10,Fstuff you're actually entitled to."
OL,12,FAfter posting his story on social
OL,13,Fmedia this week, Wayne has had calls
OL,14,Fwith social security officials to
OL,15,Fexpedite his claims process.
OL,17,FDeputy Kristina Moore also raised
OL,18,FWayne's story as part of an emergency
OL,19,Fquestion in the States' Assembly on
OL,20,FWednesday 10 December.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/9
