OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F381A1733953035
OL,3,CTerminally ill man waits two months
OL,4,Cfor social security support
OL,6,FIn response, Social Security Minister
OL,7,FLyndsay Feltham told the States: "If
OL,8,Fthe Deputy is aware of a case that she
OL,9,Fis particularly concerned about, I
OL,10,Fwould like to hear about that case so
OL,11,Fthat any matters can be resolved.
OL,13,F"I am in the middle of a review of
OL,14,Fincome support guidelines. I am
OL,15,Fmeeting with the relevant staff on a
OL,16,Ffortnightly basis.
OL,18,F"If something feels morally wrong, I
OL,19,Fwant to know about it. I want things
OL,20,Fto be resolved."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/9
