OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F381A1733953035
OL,3,CTerminally ill man waits two months
OL,4,Cfor social security support
OL,6,FThe Minister told ITV News: "I am
OL,7,Falways concerned about the length of
OL,8,Ftime processes take and I will always
OL,9,Fbe concerned if people are having to
OL,10,Fwait to receive their benefits."
OL,12,FWayne is now calling for the whole
OL,13,FSocial Security system to be reviewed.
OL,15,FHe says: "My main aim here is not to
OL,16,Fworry about my own case but to worry
OL,17,Fabout others.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/9
