PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F381A1733953035
OL,3,CTerminally ill man waits two months
OL,4,Cfor social security support
OL,6,F"There are other people out there who
OL,7,Fare terminally ill, who are going
OL,8,Fthrough what I'm going through, who
OL,9,Fare afraid to put their heads above
OL,10,Fthe parapet.
OL,12,F"Hopefully in two years' time, I'll
OL,13,Fstill be sat here and I'll still be
OL,14,Ffighting.
OL,16,F"But people with terminal illnesses
OL,17,Fneed to be treated with a little more
OL,18,Fdignity, care, and speed. Because time
OL,19,Fis not something that they've got."
